<br>
50bs,39weapon,18parry<br>
<br>
18parry <br>
+<br>
12 from RR ect<br>
___<br>
30 parry<br>
+<br>
MoParry II 6% to Parry<br>
(not sure what that works out to for your end parry skill)<br>
<br>
30 Parry + 6% to parry is alot better than bringing your Weapon down to 20. The loss of Weapon skill would hurt alot. &lt;Think about how it was lvling your skald (if u kept BS up with your lvl and remaining points into your weapon) Your dmg is horrible and you missed a whole lot.&gt;<br>
<br>
With this same templete I do very well in PvE (I parry like crazy) now factor in Shammy buffs and you will do really well.<br>
RvR I parry a bit but not even close to what I do in PvE, I don't think having a Higher parry spec would help in that situation either.<br>
<br>
